Class: StableDiffusionXLAdapterPipeline. It's a pipeline for text-to-image generation using Stable Diffusion with T2I-Adapter. It integrates adapters for additional conditioning, supports LoRA, IP adapters, textual inversion, etc. It handles encoding prompts, latents, safety checking, etc.

Business intent: Provide a high-level API for generating images from text with enhanced conditioning via adapters, enabling customization and safety, for developers building generative AI applications.

Keywords: text-to-image, stable diffusion, adapter, T2I, diffusion pipeline, latent diffusion, safety checker, LoRA, IP adapter, prompt encoding, image generation, conditional U-Net, scheduler, VAE, CLIP, multi-adapter, weighting.

Business intent: "Enable developers to easily generate high‑quality, controllable images from text while allowing fine‑grained conditioning and safety, suitable for creative tools, content generation platforms, and research prototypes."
